name: St Dalfour Strawberry Fruit Spread, 17.6 Ounce
short_description: Classic Strawberry flavor with a velvety finish and rich texture. Pairs well with shortbread, cream cheese and champagne.
Our artisanal recipe was created after the turn of the 19th century. We craft our fruit spreads south of Bordeaux, amid the renowned terroir dubbed “the Garden of France”.
We use only 100% fruit with vineyard-ripened grape 'must' as a natural sweetener.
Our Maître Confiturier uses only the finest ingredients, gently cooking carefully selected fruit and fruit juices in traditional kettles.
Our spreads are made to preserve the delicious complexity and texture of the fruit, with no artificial additives, cane sugars or preservatives ever used.
product_description: Savor the exceptional taste of St Dalfour Strawberry French Fruit Spread, meticulously crafted in France to deliver a rich, authentic flavor experience. Made with 100% fruit, this premium spread captures the vibrant essence of ripe strawberries, offering a naturally sweet and juicy delight in every bite. Free from synthetic nitrates or nitrites and without artificial additives, this spread is a pure and wholesome choice for those who appreciate the natural goodness of fruit. Sweetened solely with Fruit Juice Concentrates, it delivers a naturally indulgent sweetness without added sugars. Perfect for enhancing your favorite breakfast or dessert, it adds a gourmet touch to any meal. Sealed in a 10 oz jar to preserve its fresh, bold flavor, this spread ensures every spoonful is as delightful as the first. Elevate your culinary creations with the refined taste and quality of St Dalfour Strawberry French Fruit Spread, a true testament to French tradition and expertise.
